To integrate the nexus with maven we need to update the /opt/apache-maven-3.9.9/conf and pom.xml files as follows:

Edit the /opt/apache-maven-3.9.9/conf with following data under <servers> tag as follows:
<server>
	<id>nexus-snapshots</id>
	<username>nexusUSERNAME</username>
	<password>nexusPASSWORD</password>
</server>
<server>
	<id>nexus-releases</id>
	<username>nexusUSERNAME</username>
	<password>nexusPASSWORD</password>
</server>

Edit the pom.xml file as follows:
<distributionManagement>
	<snapshotRepository>
		<id>nexus-snapshots</id>
		<url>maven-snapshots URL</url>
	</snapshotRepository>
	<repository>
		<id>nexus-releases</id>
		<url>maven-releases URL</url>
	</repository>
</distributionManagement>
